OL,3,CSearch underway for missing Piper
OL,4,CAlpha disaster hero
OL,6,FA search is underway for a man who
OL,7,Fbecame known as a local hero after
OL,8,Fhelping to save lives in the Piper
OL,9,FAlpha oil rig disaster.
OL,11,FMike Yarwood, whose first name is
OL,12,FCharles, was a winchman for RAF
OL,13,FBoulmer and assisted rescuing people
OL,14,Fby helicopter from the fire in 1988.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police say the 78-year-old
OL,17,Fwas last seen in the Amble area, in
OL,18,FNorthumberland, on Friday night (21
OL,19,FNovember) and has issued a CCTV image
OL,20,Fbelieved to be the last sighting.
