OL,4,CAlpha disaster hero
OL,6,FIn an appeal, Northumbria Police said:
OL,7,F"A trawl of CCTV footage has led us to
OL,8,Ffind a new image of Mike, who was
OL,9,Fpictured passing the Wynd towards Beal
OL,10,FBank at around 11.30pm that evening.
OL,12,F"Our search activity continues, with
OL,13,Fthis photo believed to be our last
OL,14,Fsighting of him in the community."
OL,16,FMr Yarwood is described as a white
OL,17,Fman, 5ft 6ins tall and of average
OL,18,Fbuild with short grey hair.
