OL,3,CSearch underway for missing Piper
OL,4,CAlpha disaster hero
OL,6,FThe force said he was last seen
OL,7,Fwearing a woolly hat, a leather jacket
OL,8,Fand a head torch as captured in the
OL,9,FCCTV still below.
OL,11,FThe North Sea oil platform, the Piper
OL,12,FAlpha, exploded off the coast of
OL,13,FAberdeen in 1988.
OL,15,FIt became the world's worst off-shore
OL,16,Findustry disaster - killing 167
OL,17,Fpeople, including 17 from the North
OL,18,FEast.
